12
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:30,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: And we keep hearing greater and greater testimonies about how Unbound has been spreading and how many of you are doing the work of setting captives free.

13
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:48,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I've been asked today to share about how Unbound developed and where it's going.

14
00:01:48,000 --> 00:02:00,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: And I thought of two scriptures. One is from Psalm 127.

15
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:02,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Do you have two citata from this psalm?

16
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Which one?

17
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:05,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Psalm 127.

18
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:12,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: And it says unless the Lord builds a house, the building will be labor in vain.

19
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:16,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Koji kaže ako gospodin kuću ne gradi, uzalud se trude graditelji.

20
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:20,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: And then in Matthew 27, just one verse 24.

21
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:24,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I u Mateju, Matthew 27.

22
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:28,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Matej 27: 24.

23
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:33,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: It says therefore everyone who hears these words of mine.

24
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:36,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: I kaže svi koji čuju uve moje riječi.

25
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:42,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: And puts them into practice is like a wise man who builds this house on the rock.

26
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:47,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I vršaj svaka osoba, dakle, pokud mudrog čovjeka koji gradi svoju kuću na stijeni.

27
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:53,560
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: So when I think about the story of how Unbound came to be,

28
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:59,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: I want you to know it's not like Moses going up to the mountain

29
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:03,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: And dwelling in the glory cloud and getting the five keys.

30
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:06,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I kad razmišljam o tome kako sam Unbound razvio,

31
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:11,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Moja priča nije poput Mojsija koji je došao na goru

32
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:14,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I tamo sreo Boga i dobio spet jučeva.

33
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:23,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: It has a lot to do with my personal story and how the Lord touched my life

34
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:27,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: And how I was just simply trying to give away what he had given me.

35
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:31,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Priča je više povezana uz moj vlastiti život, uz moju vlastitu priču

36
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:35,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I sve ono što mi je gospodin dao.

37
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:48,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: To je priča o tome kako sam ja tražio veću slobodu u svom životu i kako mi je gospodin dao.

38
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:51,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I had a real hunger to help people to know Jesus.

39
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:55,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Bio sam gladan toga da pomognem ljudima da upoznaju Isusa.

40
00:03:55,000 --> 00:04:05,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: But I also knew that a lot of people following Jesus got stuck and had problems and I wanted to help.

41
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:11,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: A sam isto tako znao da mnogi ljudi koji slijede Isusa su zapeli u nekim svojim problemima i htio sam im pomoći.

42
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:18,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: And through the years I've seen a lot of harm that's been done in the body of Christ by sincere people.

43
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:28,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I kroz godine vidio sam da je mnogo štete učinjeno u Kristovu tijelu od strane iskrenih ljudi.

44
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:34,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Which helped me to be cautious enough to wait and listen for the Lord's leading.

45
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:41,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Što mi je pomoglo da budem dovoljno oprezan i da čekam i da čekam na gospodina da me on povede.

46
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:47,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: And to test what I learned by looking for fruit and evidence of God's work.

47
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:54,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I da iskušamo ono što sam naučio tako da sam čekao na potvrde odnosno dokaze, oplodove.

48
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:57,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: We really want the Lord to build a house.

49
00:04:57,000 --> 00:05:00,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Zaista želimo da gospodin gradi kuću.

50
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:10,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: And wherever we go, I'm always looking for the evidence of the Spirit so that we can invest ourselves in what he's doing.

51
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:17,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I kamo god idemo uvijek tražimo dokaze duha svetoga da bi se tamo dali.

52
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:24,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: And I've certainly seen extraordinary evidence of God working in you.

53
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:27,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: And we really do want to work with you and invest in you.

54
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:36,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I zaista vidimo izvanredno snagodjelovanje duha svetoga među vama i zato želimo i raditi s vama i dati se vama.

55
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:39,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: My passion is to see people set free.

56
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:43,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Moja strast je da vidim ljude kako bivaju oslobođeni.

57
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:46,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: First through an encounter with Jesus.

58
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Prvo kroz usred s Isusom.

59
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:56,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: And secondly to be healed and delivered and really allow Jesus and the Spirit to lead people to the Father.

60
00:05:56,000 --> 00:06:04,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: A onda kroz oslobođenje, iscijeljenje i dopuštanje Isusu da po duhu svetom osobu dovede do Otca.

61
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:08,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: So I'm just going to go over a little bit of my story.

62
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:11,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Pa ću prijeći nešto malo reći o svojoj priči.

63
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:16,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: And you've heard some of it if you've been to the Freedom in Christ conference.

64
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:19,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Ako ste prošli unbound basic, nešto ste i čuli o tome.

65
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:25,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: But I had a life changing encounter with Jesus in 1970.

66
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:29,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: 1970 imao sam susred s Isusom koji promijenio moj život.

67
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:33,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I was still with the Spirit and felt so incredibly free.

68
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:40,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: A couple years later I realized that I wasn't as free as I should be.

69
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:48,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: Nakon nekoliko godina shvatio sam da nisam slobodan koliko sam mislio, koliko sam trebao biti.

70
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:56,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: And someone prayed for me for inner healing which really had to do with deep forgiveness towards my Father.

71
00:06:56,000 --> 00:07:03,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: I netko je za mene molio za nutarni iscijeljenje koje je bilo jako vezano uz moje opraštanje mome Otcu.

72
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:05,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: But even then it was...

