00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:07,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: I should say...

74
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:14,000
[SPEAKER_04] Neal: But that was only a door that opened me to understand that I needed more freedom.

75
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:29,000
[SPEAKER_03] Neal: And it took me fifteen years before I could get the profound deliverance that I was looking for.

76
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:38,000
